name: Barn Owlz x Bora Bora Koala

metadata.name: Barn Owlz x Bora Bora Koala
metadata.description: Barn Owlz x Bora Bora Koala! A community advocating mindfulness and well-being, the Delirious Mind Travelers (DMT) consists of a set of 300 1/1 hand-drawn pieces that each have their own titles and backstory in the metadata, as well as 1500 generative Bora Bora Koalas which are the first Mysterious Delirious Mind Animal that the Delirious Mind Travelers encounter during their mind travels. The artwork for this piece was done by the Barn Owlz artist @Adamziz
